# CAM::DISABLE_CAM_COLLISION_FOR_OBJECT

## Summary
Permanently disables the camera collision for an object

## Parameters
* **OBJECT_INDEX** object

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
This will allow the camera to clip into the object.
